entries.femaleVariant: Goodness, gracious, me…
A damn shame that's that.
Always gotta ruin it?
Huh, in the mood to scrap again?
What, smoking after sex not Zen enough for you? We gotta rewrite "The Art of War," too?
Always gotta shit all over it, don't you?
YOUR moment? Why the hell not.
We're done, Johnny, with it all. I just... couldn't ghost without saying... something.
Things were swimmin'… What, change your mind? Eats at my gut.
No good for you? This? All of a sudden?
Damn, you're on my ass today.
Man, are you on my ass today.
Not just today. How is it subtlety goes so far over your head? Weird for an artist.
'Cause you knew what you were signin' up for.
Look, if you were just another charismatic, narcissistic douchecanoe running around after his dream with his head up his ass, I couldn't care less.
But?
It's all a lie. That concert, Samurai, all of it. A ginormous fiction.
Got me all figured out, don't you?
You're not a rockerboy, Johnny. Face it. Oughta join the wired wackos on the corners, frothing at the mouth as they scream "Death to Arasaka!"
Like to fix your men, do ya?
I see. Think you've seen through me, do you?
Uh-huh, I get it! Like to fix your men, huh? Not the first to try, believe me.
You know exactly what I mean. Look at you – faking it even to yourself.
Huh, probably what you're best at – faking it.
Honestly? I've got better things to do. Just hoped I'd help you realize you're deluding yourself.
An' that doing anything about it… that's on you.
You're confused. Get the fuck out of here.
You're confused. We came here to fuck each other's brains out, not analyze mine.
Afraid of Arasaka, that's what you are.
Think we're done for the day, so you can fuck off.
Mmmhm.
Any moment that might actually feel good.
You don't have to ghost.
So say it.
So go on – say it.
You don't gotta ghost. I'll always--
...gladly fuck you when there's no one else around who wants to?
That's the idea!
Isn't that what you came for?
Guess you got fucky lucky today.
Isn't that exactly why you're here?
Mh. You're afraid. You and Kerry both – cowards.
'Course. Johnny S. – misunderstood by all Night City. That's it, that's the problem.
See, I thought…
[Grab] That this meant something? Well, aren't you imaginative.
Just stop talking.
Not another goddamn word, OK? Just shut up. For once.
You're fucking hopeless.
That this meant something? That we're close? So close you can give me shit about everything I do?
Got quite the imagination, then.
You don't know fuck all about me. This is all we have, all we are.
I alone have the balls to stand up to Arasaka. And boy, that terrifies you – all of you.
You can be such a bastard sometimes, Johnny.
[Take] Think we're done here. Fuck off.
Slow spinning mental cogs?
Johnny?
